	depends on SMP
	select SCHED_SMT
	select SCHED_MC
	select SCHED_BOOK
	select SCHED_DRAWER
	help
	  Topology scheduler support improves the CPU scheduler's decision
	  making when dealing with machines that have multi-threading,
	  multiple cores or multiple books.

